name: Banana Cream OG
description: Banana Cream OG is grown by Vagrant Hill Farms of Forest Grove, Oregon. This strain is a hybrid cross of Blue Dream, Banana OG, and Ocean Beach OG. It emits strong notes of orange and spearmint, and expresses tight lime green buds. Not much more is known about this strain other than its heavy, OG-forward effects that lay into the body and gain weight with continued consumption.

highlightedReviews.text:
I was excited to try this strain because of the Blue Dream lineage. Boy was this a tasty strain.  Very good high that left me feeling relaxed but also energetic.  

I love the flavors too. The minty +pine scent was very refreshing.

I wasn’t sure what I thought about this strain until anxiety and depression put it to the test very recently. I woke up very upset (in tears) over a breakup, and reached for my vape pen which had a cartridge of  Naked brand Banana Cream OG (90% thc distillate) attached. I went from sobbing to perky and happy to be awake. That was about 20 mins ago, and now that I’m writing this review, I  can’t remember why I was ever upset in the first place. Thank you, Banana Cream!  
 Ratings:
Taste/terps—  5.0/5.0
Depression— 5.0/5.0
Stress & Anxiety— 4.75/5.0
Insomnia—   3.0/5.0
Pain—  4.0/5.0
Appetite—  3.75/5.0

Overall: 4.25/5.0 highly recommend for depression
